"Most [[Open Education]] initiatives to date were launched by well established universities in the West. Phillip Schmidt from the University of Western Cape introduces the student-led RipMixLearners project at UWC and discusses the lack of funding for [[Open Educational Resources]] (OER) in Africa. We also talked about peer 2 peer university, which is set to launch in early 2009."


